text: Helcystogramma chalybea is a moth in the family Gelechiidae. It was described by Cajetan Felder, Rudolf Felder and Alois Friedrich Rogenhofer in 1875. It is found in Brazil.Helcystogramma at Markku Savela's Lepidoptera and Some Other Life Forms ==References== Category:Moths described in 1875 chalybea Category:Moths of Brazil
title: Helcystogramma chalybea
